</span><span class="lsb">“和尚还在，</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y152 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">可我到哪儿去了？” </div><div class="t m0 x22 h4 y1b7 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">现在世间上的很多人，<span class="_ _5"></span>也像这个公差一样，<span class="_ _5"></span>没日没夜地</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y1b8 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">忙着各种琐事，<span class="_ _4"></span>不知不觉中，<span class="_ _4"></span>将自己变成了囚徒，<span class="_ _4"></span>结果<span class="_ _4"></span>“我”</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y154 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">却找不到了。 </div><div class="t m0 x22 h4 y1b5 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">就像如今的有些学者，<span class="_ _5"></span>一辈子都在研究这个课题、<span class="_ _5"></span>那个</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
